metadata.name: $Pepe Charts (Limited Editions)
metadata.description:
Your $Pepe Charts (Limited) Editions is your entry way into the mind of davie and his popular elliott wave charts. Collect davie's $Pepe Charts Edition and gain token-gated entry into his private discord channel and get first look at his EW charts and analysis on $pepe. Meet like minded members to discuss everything $pepe and learn from each other.  Depending on the membership tier, each member will gain benefits and insight on $pepe and also their favorite NFT project. 

Disclaimer: This is not financial advice nor an investment club. This is merely entry to a discord channel where like minded people discuss about a hobby they have in common. By purchasing an edition, you agree that you are responsible for any financial action you take and you will not hold anyone in the channel or the project creators and managers accountable for any of your financial actions. This project does not promote the sale or use of $pepe and has no connection with the creators of $pepe, Matt Furie or any political or investment organization. The opinions and intentions of this project is for fun.
